- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a visual model for recognizing protesters and estimating perceived violence in images. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper analyzes geotagged tweets and their images to study protest events. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with analyzing images and their attributes. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper deals with analyzing social media data and detecting protest activity.
